                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9837" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0261</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">688 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通汇物流：商用车全生命周期一体化供应链生态圈构建之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tonghui Logistics: The Road to Building an Integrated Supply Chain Ecosystem for the Whole Life Cycle of Commercial Vehicles </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李倩，李慧敏，王智</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长安大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西通汇汽车物流有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通汇物流；一体化物流；全生命周期；数智化赋能；一体化供应链生态圈</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tonghui Logistics; Integrated Logistics; Whole Life Cycle; Digitalization Empowerment; Integrated Supply Chain Ecosystem</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球数字化转型进程加速的背景下，商用车物流行业正经历着前所未有的变革，面临着多重挑战，传统物流模式已难以满足日益复杂的市场需求。本案例描述了通汇物流从一体化物流模式到全生命周期一体化供应链生态圈的转型之路，通汇物流作为陕汽集团的旗下企业，面对外部机遇与挑战，先后通过三阶段的突破式跃升实现了发展模式的革新，首先通过信息系统升级集成整合供应链数据，建立供应链一体化物流模式；继而从运输、仓储和配送环节入手，进行数智化赋能推动一体化物流模式升级；最终在一体化物流模式的基础上，围绕商用车全生命周期，协同上下游合作伙伴，整合全产业链资源，走上一体化供应链生态圈的构建之路。本案例可以引导学员思考传统物流模式存在的弊端、商用车供应链一体化物流模式的优势、一体化供应链生态圈的构建路径，同时为商用车及制造业物流转型升级提供借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of accelerating global digital transformation, the commercial vehicle logistics industry is undergoing unprecedented changes and facing multiple challenges. Traditional logistics models can no longer meet the increasingly complex market demands. This case describes the transformation of Tonghui Logistics from an integrated logistics model to a whole - life - cycle integrated supply chain ecosystem. As a subsidiary of Shanqi Company, Tonghui Logistics has successively achieved breakthroughs in three stages to renew its development model in the face of external opportunities and challenges. First, it upgraded and integrated information systems to consolidate supply chain data and establish an integrated supply chain logistics model. Then, it started from the transportation, warehousing, and distribution links, empowered by digital intelligence to promote the upgrading of the integrated logistics model. Finally, based on the integrated logistics model, it focused on the whole life cycle of commercial vehicles, coordinated with upstream and downstream partners, integrated the entire industry chain resources, and embarked on the road of building an integrated supply chain ecosystem. This case can guide students to think about the drawbacks of traditional logistics models, the advantages of the integrated logistics model for commercial vehicle supply chains, and the construction road of the integrated supply chain ecosystem. It also provides references and examples for the transformation and upgrading of logistics in commercial vehicles and manufacturing industries.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">供应链一体化理论；数智化赋能理论；供应链生态圈理论；供应链协同理论；供应链生态圈治理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
